The paper deals with optimization methods for segmentation and reconstruction, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses bias in learning and proposes solutions, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions stereo reconstruction, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
